梅仲明可能并不知道这种传染病的危害也没做很好的防护武汉市中心医院医护人员参加抗击新冠疫情。
Mei Zhongming probably did not know the hazards of the epidemic and did not do a good job of protection Wuhan City Central Hospital medical staff to fight the new crown epidemic.
（图片来源：央视截屏）今天下午，武汉市中心医院发布公告称，该院眼科副主任、主任医师梅仲明，在抗击新冠肺炎疫情工作中不幸染病，经全力抢救无效，于2020年3月3日中午12时在武汉市金银潭医院去世，享年57岁。
(Photo: CCTV Interview) This afternoon, Wuhan Central Hospital issued a notice saying that the hospital's deputy ophthalmologist and chief physician, Li Zhongming, died at 12: 00 noon on March 3, 2020 at the Jiantan Hospital in Wuhan, aged 57.
梅仲明是此前去世的中心医院医生李文亮同科室的同事，这也是该医院自疫情暴发以来痛失的第三名医生。
Li Wenliang, a doctor at the central hospital who died earlier, is the third doctor in the hospital to suffer since the outbreak.
网上传出门牌上写着“主任梅仲明，医师李文亮”的照片，展示的场景正是李文亮与梅仲明生前在武汉中心医院南京路院区的办公室。
A picture of Li Wenliang and Mei Zhongming, doctors Li Wenliang, written on the Web, shows the offices of Li Wenliang and Mei Zhongming in the Nanjing Road courtyard area of Wuhan Central Hospital.
医院公告称，梅仲明1962年11月29日出生于湖北省武汉市。
Mei Zhongming was born in Wuhan, Hubei Province, on November 29, 1962, a hospital notice said.
1986年7月从中山医科大学临床医学专业毕业后，一直在武汉市中心医院眼科工作。
Since graduating from Zhongshan Medical University in July 1986, he has been working as an ophthalmologist in Wuhan Central Hospital.
梅仲明从医30余年，工作认真负责，对患者耐心细致，为学科建设发展作出重要贡献。
Mei Zhongming has been a doctor for more than 30 years. He works conscientiously and conscientiously and makes great contributions to the development of discipline construction.
公开资料显示，梅仲明生前担任湖北省眼科学会委员、武汉市眼科学会委员、湖北省防盲专家小组成员。
She was a member of the Hubei Ophthalmology Society, Wuhan Ophthalmology Society and Hubei Provincial Blindness Prevention Expert Group.
有数千例白内障超声乳化吸出术及人工晶体植入术经验。
There were thousands of cases of phacoemulsification and intraocular lens implantation.
擅长青光眼、白内障、眼后段等疾病的诊断、治疗，是香港“健康快车”武汉站的主要手术者之一，曾荣获武汉市“光明特使”称号。
Specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of glaucoma, cataract, posterior segment of the eye, and other diseases, Hong Kong "Health Express" Wuhan station is one of the main surgeons, has been awarded the Wuhan "special envoy of light."
武汉市中心医院的医生刘嘉敏称，梅仲明在李文亮感染后不久即出现症状，患病后也没有好好休息，还给其他患者开刀做了手术。
Liu Jiamin, a doctor at Wuhan Central Hospital, said MeiZhongming developed symptoms shortly after his infection, did not get a good rest and had surgery on other patients.
她推测，当时，梅仲明可能并不知道这种传染病的危害，也没做很好的防护。
At the time, she speculated, Mei probably did not know the hazards of the epidemic and was not well protected.
刘嘉敏说，梅仲明在住院后辗转了多个地方接受治疗，起初，他在医院南京路院区的综合科病房住院，之后转移到南京路院区呼吸科的隔离病房，再被转移到汉口医院、中心医院后湖院区呼吸科监护室继续治疗。
He was hospitalized in a polyclinic on Nanjing Road, then moved to the respiratory ward of the Nanjing Road hospital and was transferred to Hankou Hospital and the Respiratory Care Unit at the back of the central hospital, Liu said.
李文亮去世后，梅仲明到金银潭医院接受救治。
After Li Wenliang died, Mei Zhongming went to the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital for treatment.
李浩是武汉中心医院的一名护士，在后湖院区没有成为发热病人定点收治医院时，曾去汉口医院支援。
Li Hao, a nurse at Wuhan Central Hospital, went to Hankou Hospital to support him when the hospital did not become a designated hospital for febrile patients.
1月24日大年三十晚上，他在汉口医院见到了正在住院的梅仲明，同病房还有另外两名中心医院的职工，这是李浩第一次见到梅仲明，也是最后一次。
On the evening of January 24, he met with Mezhong Ming in Hankou Hospital and two other staff from the central hospital. This was Li's first and last visit to Mei Zhongming.
李浩称，当时感觉梅仲明呼吸比较困难，当晚12点左右，梅仲明被转往后湖院区。
Li said that it was difficult to feel Mei Zhongming breathing, that night around 12 o'clock, Mei Zhongming was transferred back to the Lake District.
李浩帮着梅仲明洗碗、收拾行李、再将其扶至轮椅送出病区，在他印象里，感觉梅仲明是做事很有条理的人，也热爱生活，会自己带着电饭煲热饭。
Li helps Mei Zhongming wash dishes, pack his luggage and take him out of the sick area. He has the impression that Mei Zhongming is a very organized person who loves life and cooks his own hot rice with rice cookers.
在刘嘉敏的印象中，梅仲明人很好、低调，踏踏实实工作，身体结实，很少得病。
In Liu Jiamin's impression, Mezhong Ming people are very good, low-key, down-to-earth work, strong body, rarely get sick.
2000年前后举行的香港“健康快车”武汉站活动中，梅仲明曾给很多经济条件不好的白内障患者开刀，费用很便宜，救了很多人。
During the "Healthy Express" Wuhan Station held around 2000, Mei Zhongming operated on a number of cataract patients with poor economic conditions, saving many lives at low cost.
梅仲明是中心医院继眼科医生李文亮，以及甲状腺乳腺外科党支部书记、主任、主任医师、中国医师奖获得者江学庆之后第三位因感染新冠肺炎去世的医生。
Mei Zhongming is the third doctor to die of pneumonia in the central hospital after ophthalmologist Li Wenliang, secretary, director, chief physician and Chinese physician-award winner Jiang Xueqing.
年仅34岁的李文亮经全力抢救无效，于2020年2月7日凌晨2点58分去世。
Li Wenliang, 34 years old, died at 2.58 a.m. on February 7, 2020 after trying his best to save him.
江学庆于2020年3月1日凌晨5点32分去世，享年55岁。
Jiang Xueqing died at 5: 32 am on March 1, 2020, aged 55.
另据《中国新闻周刊》了解，武汉市中心医院多名科室主任在新冠肺炎疫情中出现感染。
According to "China News Weekly," the director of the central hospital in Wuhan City was infected with the new crown pneumonia.
心胸外科一名副主任医师以及一名泌尿外科副主任医师过去两天因为病情较重都被相继转往华中科技大学附属同济医院中法新城院区救治，其中，泌尿外科副主任医师正在准备接受肺移植。
A deputy head of cardiology and a deputy urologist have been transferred to the French-Xincheng Hospital of Tongji Hospital attached to the Central China University of Science and Technology for treatment in the past two days because of his serious condition.
（文中刘嘉敏、李浩为化名）值班编辑：俞杨推荐阅读▼日本“以举国之力向中国提供支援”背后研究生紧急扩招，考研党速效救心封面报道《新冠病毒——我们要付出多大代价》《围城之战——我们如何过关》《武汉攻坚——我们如何与疫情赛跑》《防控之辨——我们怎样科学应对》点击下图，一键下单。
